{"tid":318779,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"強國食客用 IPhone 打邊爐 ?? 事主要求食店賠償","createTime":"2017-07-12T10:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T10:37:43.000Z","uid":86425,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2249358e3f4e011970e843c229b5b0398ed582d","tid":318779,"uid":86425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2843895643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F2843895643.jpg&h=6786c093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n神州大地無奇不怪 , 各種奇人奇事大家都見得多 , 可有見過用 iPhone 來打邊爐(即火鍋) ? 在 7月10日 , 在上海的一間火鍋店就發生了一宗十分有趣的新聞 .<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F5654.jpg&h=42394b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主汪小姐與同事於下班後到了一家火鍋店就餐 , 而當時店家就聯同支付寶旗下《口碑》評價搞了活動 , 在店消費就可以用支付寶掃瞄 QR Code 可以得到隨機金額的紅包 . 誰不之事主抽中了 999元的大獎 , 一時興奮之下竟手上一鬆 , iPhone 就掉到了麻辣的湯中 .<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/546456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F546456.jpg&h=747a7d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主汪小姐認為這個意外是這個活動造成 , 商家或《口碑》平台理應賠償她一部iPhone .<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉自Qooah<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/07/12/china-iphone-hot-pot/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2Fchina-iphone-hot-pot%2F&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q5x4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=ec54727c\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/07/12/china-iphone-hot-pot/</a>"},{"pid":"87d69f39191216e8d5a74ae213e07e05d13dcf00","tid":318779,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"啱呀，大陸係咁㗎喇"},{"pid":"7a301497d83a8dfe262222f042b455b4f1754d1d","tid":318779,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor